name: Laptop + camera messenger bag
description:
Messenger style bag with a padded insert for DSLR / SLR camera. The bag is made with dark gray/black tweed look fabric. This bag has two exterior pockets securely placed under the flap + two spacious pockets with flaps, one at each end of the bag. Dedicated laptop compartment inside comes with a snap closure. Lining is made with sturdy 100% cotton canvas. 

The bag comes with a gray removable padded insert for a camera, 2-3 lenses and a flash, as well as a flat pocket for a tablet, manuals, cords etc. The insert has two adjustable dividers with velcro attachment.

The comfortable 2" wide black seatbelt webbing strap is fully adjustable between approx. 55" and 28".

Outside dimensions of the bag:

Height: 9 1/4" (23.5cm)
Width: 13 1/2" (34cm)
Depth: 6" (15cm)

Size of padded insert:

Height: 9" (23cm)
Width: 13" (32.5cm)

name: Medium DSLR camera bag with padded insert in dark denim
description:
Stylish medium size messenger style bag for SLR / DSLR camera. The bag is made with dark blue denim and lined with sturdy water-resistant off white canvas.

The bag comes with loads of pockets for all the small accessories. On the outside the bag has two rivet reinforced pockets under the flap, one pocket at each end of the bag and two pockets on the back side. Inside there are 4 more pockets.

The bag comes with a removable padded canvas insert for the camera and lenses. The insert has two adjustable dividers with velcro attachment.

The last picture shows the bag loaded with Canon T1i with small lens attached, plus an 18-55mm lens, a 75-300mm zoom lens, USB cable, batteries and a Speedlite flash.

The comfortable black 2" wide seat belt webbing strap is fully adjustable between 55" and 28". 

Please note that as with any denim product, color transfer may occur on light colored clothes or furniture.

Size:

Height: 7 1/4" (18.5cm)
Width: 10 1/4" (26cm)
Depth: 5 1/2" (14cm)

Insert size:

Height: 7" (16.5cm)
Width: 10" (25.5cm)
Depth: 5" (12.5cm)
